cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.GR 

This paper deals with deep learning-based methods for 3D registration of medical images, which involves computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of geodesic loss, which is a common optimization technique in artificial intelligence (AI) research. Additionally, the paper focuses on medical imaging, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.MED and cs.GR (graphics).
